cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about dialogue systems and natural language processing, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The retrieval-based model proposed in the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the use of a topic coherence discrimination model, which is related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
